seo: Weblogic,漏洞检测,CVE-2020-14883,远程代码执行
summary: 该插件用于检测Weblogic服务器是否存在CVE-2020-14883漏洞，即Weblogic Console HTTP协议远程代码执行漏洞。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the Weblogic server has the CVE-2020-14883 vulnerability, which is a Remote Code Execution vulnerability in the Weblogic Console HTTP protocol.
